  "readme": "Superpowers is a complete software development methodology for your coding agents. It provides a complete agentic skills framework and methodology. The repository includes reusable skills, command hooks, plugin manifests, and installable integrations. Workflows include brainstorming, writing plans, TDD, systematic debugging, requesting code review, and verification. Plugin and skill files let different coding agents load the same workflow instructions. Quickstart: install the plugin and use skills.",
